<h2 class="bold font-l">Ueno Beats Up Shouko</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Shouya gets into a coma after saving Shouko from committing suicide. When Ueno finds out, she goes apeshit and beats up Shouko at the lowest point in her life, telling her she should have died instead. Because that's clearly how you should treat someone who's not only deaf, but suicidal and with rock bottom self-esteem and self-worth! </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/KickTheDog" class='trope-example-link'>Kick the Dog</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="8invi5" data-video-descrip="Shouko, a deaf girl, was mercilessly bullied by other kids when she was in sixth grade." data-video-title="Shouko Nishimiya" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/8invi5_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/8invi5.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/BullyingTheDisabled" data-video-tropename="Bullying the Disabled" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Manga/ASilentVoice" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/8invi5.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Shouko Nishimiya</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="xr5pfp" data-video-descrip="Blaming herself for Shoya being admitted into a hospital after falling into a coma saving her, Shoko tears up, stating how the situation was all her fault." data-video-title="Shoko Nishimiya" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/xr5pfp_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/xr5pfp.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TearsOfRemorse" data-video-tropename="Tears of Remorse" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Manga/ASilentVoice" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/xr5pfp.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Shoko Nishimiya</span></p>
