<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Ueno Beats Up Shouko</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Shouya gets into a coma after saving Shouko from committing suicide. When Ueno finds out, she goes apeshit and beats up Shouko at the lowest point in her life, telling her she should have died instead. Because that's clearly how you should treat someone who's not only deaf, but suicidal and with rock bottom self-esteem and self-worth!	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="5v3xjw">
